QT5 Client for MPD (the Music Player Daemon).

Features include:

* Support for (offline) albumart.
* Support for audio streams (url).
* Support for files that are not is MPD's database ('Drag&Drop' or 'Open With').
* Drag & Drop playlist management and arrangement.
* Library browser (artist, album, genre, year, modified, folder & playlist mode)
* Library search (artist, album, genre, title & folder mode).
* Quick search-and-select in the playlist.
* Mini-Mode interface for basic control only.
* Open folder in external programs of choice (Tag Editor, File Manager etc.).
* Generally a powerful but quick and 'light' application.
